ning the results from step 2 and step 3, we get ∫(2x + 1) dx = x^2 + x + C, where C is the constant of integration.\n\nThe final answer is: $\\boxed{x^2 + x + C}$\n\nVerify the solution and respond with JSON only.'}], 'model': 'llama-3.3-70b-versatile', 'max_tokens': 600, 'temperature': 0.1}}
